00:53:03,158 --> 00:53:05,368
Aku bisa saja buta warna.

778
00:53:05,368 --> 00:53:06,598
Dolar?

779
00:53:06,598 --> 00:53:08,518
Bagaimana aku bisa percaya bahwa itu nyata?

780
00:53:11,538 --> 00:53:14,518
