...aku tak pernah menduga ini...

787
00:54:11,298 --> 00:54:12,408
Ayah.

788
00:54:12,408 --> 00:54:13,468
Kenapa?

789
00:54:14,618 --> 00:54:16,368
Kau sudah makan?

790
00:54:16,368 --> 00:54:17,918
Ada apa?

791
00:54:19,068 --> 00:54:21,688
Kau tahu ayah mencintaimu, bukan?

792
00:54:22,638 --> 00:54:24,948
Kenapa ekspresi ayah begitu?

793
00:54:25,778 --> 00:54:26,808
Kau tahu, bukan?

794
00:54:51,188 --> 00:54:53,048
Kenapa Ma Daepyo...

795
00:54:54,158 --> 00:54:55,938
